---
// src/components/Testimonials.astro
---
<section class="py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-200 to-transparent"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">
                Loved by local businesses.
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                We don't sell "SEO services." We sell <strong class="text-slate-900">market dominance</strong>. 
                Here is what happens when you own the map.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 relative group">
                <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 text-slate-200 group-hover:text-blue-100 transition-colors">
                    <i data-lucide="quote" class="w-8 h-8 fill-current"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-6 gap-0.5">
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">
                    "I operate in Bangsar, but my phone rings for jobs in TTDI and Damansara. The <span class="text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-1 rounded">GPS technology</span> bridged the gap. I'm not just a local shop anymore; I serve the whole district."
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200/60">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-700 font-bold text-sm">H</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
                            Hafiz A.
                            <i data-lucide="badge-check" class="w-3 h-3 text-blue-500"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Interior Designer</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 relative group">
                <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 text-slate-200 group-hover:text-blue-100 transition-colors">
                    <i data-lucide="quote" class="w-8 h-8 fill-current"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-6 gap-0.5">
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">
                    "It's unfair to my competitors. While they fight over one keyword, I have <span class="text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-1 rounded">50 different pages</span> catching customers from every corner of the city. I stopped running Ads entirely."
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200/60">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-700 font-bold text-sm">C</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
                            Chee Meng
                            <i data-lucide="badge-check" class="w-3 h-3 text-blue-500"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">HVAC Specialist</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 relative group">
                <div class="absolute top-8 right-8 text-slate-200 group-hover:text-blue-100 transition-colors">
                    <i data-lucide="quote" class="w-8 h-8 fill-current"></i>
                </div>

                <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-6 gap-0.5">
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-4 h-4 fill-current"></i>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">
                    "My competitors have 5 reviews. I show up with <span class="text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-1 rounded">Gold Stars</span> right in the search results. Clients tell me they clicked because I looked like the 'safest choice' immediately."
                </p>
                
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200/60">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-700 font-bold text-sm">S</div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
                            Sarah J.
                            <i data-lucide="badge-check" class="w-3 h-3 text-blue-500"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Event Planner</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>